DTSTART:20260721T193000Z
DTEND:20260721T203000Z
SUMMARY:CW: TTC (Tuesday's Telegraphy Contest)
DESCRIPTION:Tuesday's Telegraphy Contest\nYou send: 599 001\nSend RST + serial. Same station may be worked again each 15-minute period (4 periods per hour).\nBands: 80, 40m\nRules: https://spcwc.pl/ttc/rules/en
URL:https://mashu.github.io/cw-contest-radar/contests/ttc/
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:awt-20260722T114500Z@cw-contest-radar
DTSTAMP:20260721T084405Z
DTSTART:20260722T114500Z
DTEND:20260722T130000Z
SUMMARY:CW: AWT (A1Club AWT)
DESCRIPTION:A1Club AWT\nYou send: 599 MATEUSZ\nSend RST + your CW name (handle). First 15 minutes are QRS (≤15 wpm).\nBands: 160, 80, 40, 20, 15, 10m\nRules: https://a1club.org/contest/awt/
URL:https://mashu.github.io/cw-contest-radar/contests/awt/
END:VEVENT
