DTEND:20260916T130000Z
SUMMARY:CW: AWT (A1Club AWT)
DESCRIPTION:A1Club AWT\nYou send: 599 MATEUSZ\nSend RST + your CW name (handle). First 15 minutes are QRS (≤15 wpm).\nBands: 160, 80, 40, 20, 15, 10m\nRules: https://a1club.org/contest/awt/
URL:https://mashu.github.io/cw-contest-radar/contests/awt/
