SUMMARY:CW: CWT (CWops Mini-CWT Test)
DESCRIPTION:CWops Mini-CWT Test\nYou send: MATEUSZ SO\nNo RST. CWops members send name + member number; you send name + your prefix/country. It runs fast, but ops will slow to your speed if you call slower.\nBands: 80, 40, 20, 15, 10m\nRules: https://cwops.org/cwops-tests/
URL:https://mashu.github.io/cw-contest-radar/contests/cwt/
